    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it to get you where you need to go comfortably. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being super reliable while still looking great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
      "price": 34500.0,
