    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, this driver-focused machine offers unparalleled visceral feedback. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a variable M differential lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to optimize both longitudinal and lateral dynamics. Maintained with enthusiast care, the individual throttle bodies provide crisp induction notes, while the high-pressure VANOS system ensures a broad, usable powerband. This example has undergone key preventative maintenance, including throttle actuator servicing, ensuring the mechanical integrity of this high-revving icon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
