    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes a wonderful balance between performance and everyday practicality, having been thoughtfully maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish that catches the light beautifully, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a clean and inviting space; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, featuring a responsive engine and a transmission that shifts smoothly through every gear. It has a full service history, recent fluid changes, and tires with plenty of life left in the tread. This is a dependable, well-sorted car that is ready for its next chapter without needing immediate work.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
